      <div class="msgContentFrame">I have used Conjurer heal with some pretty good success. It has saved me several times on leves. Cure isn't that great for grinding but I have found its a pretty effective hate generator and tanking skill(Guard/Phallanx and Cure holds aggro pretty well). I heal for about 150. I have read Punishing Barbs works even on Disciples of War but I haven't tested it for myself yet. The problem with using Defender with Gladiator is we don't get access to Steadfast. It still may be effective for the defense bonus though. <br /> <br />Also I have yet to run out of mana on a leve yet, they tend to be very short. Even while grinding I keep Cure on to save myself in dire situations, I just use it more sparingly. <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Sep 25th 2010  6:31pm by Brentmeister </span></i></div>
