      <div class="msgContentFrame">About the Rank you write, now Cure is rank 4 not 6 and Stoneskin is 6 not 8 ^^ <br /> <br />For Punishing Barbs, i got it on my Action bars but only for &quot;problem&quot;, it's not really a good spell to use on every fight. For now, in FFXIV there is no reason to kill a mob only for kill it, you mostly want to gain SP even in Leves I never saw someone wanting to do a Leves only for the reward, ppl want the bonus of SP you can gain from it. So when you use Punishing Barbs the mob died to fast and you dont get a lot of SP... So the only time its good to use is in a pinch like to much mob on you, someone in the party died... <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Nov 18th 2010  8:20am by Mahouneko </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/965232.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
